reviewText: While I object to Digiview blurring the blackface scene in Fresh Hare, what took me by surprise was Jerky Turkey, since only a few MGM cartoons are in public domain. This has a little bit of everything: numerous Warner Bros. cartoons, a bit of Van Beuren, and some Fleischer cartoons with NTA titles, as well as the lone MGM cartoon (this version, however, does not have the opening MGM lion).
